videos.headline: Curtis throws pick-6 to Robertson for LA Tech TD
videos.description: Michael Curtis has his pass intercepted by LA Tech's Amik Robertson who treks 42 yards to score a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Curtis throws pick-6 to Robertson for LA Tech TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: LA Tech's Henderson bursts free for 74-yard TD
videos.description: Justin Henderson takes the handoff then jets 74 yards downfield to score a LA Tech touchdown to give them a 14-0 lead over UMass.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (LA Tech's Henderson bursts free for 74-yard TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET
